"  I read the review of this soup in the New Times 2007 "Best Of..." and have to agree that it's one of the better chicken soups around .
Perfectly salted (meaning not overly salty) and with the right amount of pepper.
Nice big chunks of obviously 100% "REAL" chicken breast (no fillers, nothing fake about it ) and zucchini and whole baby carrots.
Sprinkled with a touch of corn and rice and small slivers of onion.
Very tasty combo of flavors.
Hits the spot on a cold 50 degree day.
